AI hallucination isn’t malicious.
It’s evidential collapse.

It outputs fluent statements without:
	•	Source class
	•	Confidence band
	•	Falsification condition

You solve hallucination not by silencing it —
but by forcing evidential tagging.

That’s Matis-style cognition as infrastructure.

